headline: 2 Reasons to Watch HIG and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Hartford currently trades at $124.27 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a small loss of 1.1%. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 21.3% gain during that period.
